{"word":"G5235 - ὑπερβάλλω - hyperbállō - hoop-er-bal'-lo - Exceeding","slug":"G5235","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑπερβάλλω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>hyperbállō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>hoop-er-bal'-lo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Exceeding"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C5;&#x0314;&#x03C0;&#x03B5;&#x03C1;&#x03B2;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03BB;&#x03BB;&#x03C9; - huperballo&#x0304;</b> - <i>hoop-er-bal'-lo</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G5228\">G5228</a> and <a href=\"#/G906\">G906</a>; to <i>throw beyond</i> the usual mark, that is, (figuratively) to <i>surpass</i> (only active participle <i>supereminent</i>): - exceeding, excel, pass."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G5234\">G5234</a>, <a href=\"#/G5236\">G5236</a>"}]}